# 🧅 Pre-configured Tor daemon settings for Aether Ghost OS
SocksPort 127.0.0.1:9050
SocksPort 127.0.0.1:9051

# Route local DNS requests through Tor to prevent DNS leaks
DNSPort 127.0.0.1:9053

# Optimise circuit rotations for rapid location changes
